name: Work UI Demo 200+ Components with 147 Screens Includes
description:
Work UI is a Business app iOS UI Kit for Figma.


The kit includes 147 stylish screens and hundreds of components to help you ship your next product faster.


Types of screens included: Onboarding, Sign in/Sign up, Dashboard, Content creation, Chat, Projects, Tasks and Settings.
